sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Inference Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant vLLMMetrics as vLLM Metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant vLLMKV as vLLM KV Events<br/>5556/TCP ZMQ
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>8000/TCP
    participant Sidecar as P/D Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as Prefiller Pod<br/>configurable/TCP
    participant Decoder as Local Decoder<br/>8001/TCP

    Note over EPP,K8sAPI: Startup: Controller-Runtime Watches
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pod,<br/>InferenceObjective, InferenceModelRewrite CRs<br/>(SA token auth, TLS 1.2+)
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: CR events (add/update/delete)

    Note over EPP,vLLMKV: Background: Metrics & KV Event Collection
    EPP->>vLLMMetrics: Scrape Prometheus metrics<br/>(queue size, running reqs, KV cache %)<br/>Optional TLS
    vLLMMetrics-->>EPP: Metric values
    vLLMKV->>EPP: ZMQ PUB KV cache events<br/>(plaintext, 5556/TCP)
    Note over EPP: Update KV cache index<br/>& endpoint attribute map

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request Routing
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Gateway->>EPP: ext_proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC bidirectional stream<br/>9002/TCP (Optional TLS)
    Note over EPP: Run scheduling pipeline:<br/>1. Profile selection<br/>2. Filters (capacity, model match)<br/>3. Scorers (KV cache, load)<br/>4. Picker (select endpoint)
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>Set target-endpoint header<br/>with selected pod IP:port
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward request to<br/>selected model server<br/>HTTP/8000

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated P/D Inference
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Gateway->>EPP: ext_proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC/9002
    Note over EPP: Schedule with P/D profile:<br/>Select decode pod + prefill pod
    EPP-->>Gateway: Set target-endpoint +<br/>x-prefill-host headers
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward to decode pod's sidecar<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP (TLS 1.2+)
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: Forward prefill request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (SSRF validated)<br/>x-prefill-host target
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response +<br/>KV cache transfer params
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Decode request with<br/>KV cache reference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8001/TCP
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streamed response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Streamed response
    Gateway-->>Client: Streamed response

    Note over EPP,vLLMKV: Flow 3: KV Cache Event Subscription
    vLLMKV->>EPP: KV cache block events<br/>ZMQ PUB/SUB 5556/TCP<br/>No encryption, No auth
    Note over EPP: Index KV cache blocks<br/>for precise prefix<br/>cache scoring
